01:11:40,629 --> 01:11:43,632
I'll do whatever I can to help.
I'm sorry.

1018
01:11:43,632 --> 01:11:45,501
All right, all right, all right.
Sit tight.

1019
01:11:45,501 --> 01:11:46,991
We'll take care of everything.

1020
01:12:06,922 --> 01:12:10,192
It's, uh...
all clear out here, Frankie.

1021
01:12:10,192 --> 01:12:13,195
OK, Emilio. Let me know
if you see anything.

1022
01:12:13,195 --> 01:12:14,355
10-4.

1023
01:12:18,000 --> 01:12:20,491
- We'll call you if we need you.
- OK.

1024
01:12:28,610 --> 01:12:31,580
It's going to be OK, Spike.

1025
01:12:31,580 --> 01:12:33,571
Everything's
going to be all right.

1026
01:15:18,180 --> 01:15:19,306
Get in!

1027
01:15:35,764 --> 01:15:37,232
Let me out!

1028
01:15:37,232 --> 01:15:40,035
I just need you long enough
to get Max to follow us to Emax.

1029
01:15:40,035 --> 01:15:42,538
- Then you can go to hell.
- Stop the car!

1030
01:15:42,538 --> 01:15:44,306
Stop it!

1031
01:15:44,306 --> 01:15:46,740
Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!

1032
01:15:52,314 --> 01:15:53,615
Why didn't you leave me alone?

1033
01:15:53,615 --> 01:15:54,917
What about those animals
at your lab?

1034
01:15:54,917 --> 01:15:56,318
What about
what you're doing to them?

1035
01:15:56,318 --> 01:15:59,154
They mean nothing.
The project is what's important.

1036
01:15:59,154 --> 01:16:00,622
Don't you understand that?

1037
01:16:00,622 --> 01:16:02,724
- No. I can't.
- Gimme that.

1038
01:16:02,724 --> 01:16:06,461
You broke the bond with Max.

1039
01:16:06,461 --> 01:16:08,895
If I don't sedate him,
he's going to turn on you...

1040
01:16:09,798 --> 01:16:11,493
just like he did on me.

1041
01:16:38,427 --> 01:16:40,929
Max! Max!

1042
01:16:40,929 --> 01:16:44,600
Release! Max! Release!

1043
01:16:44,600 --> 01:16:46,368
Release!

1044
01:16:46,368 --> 01:16:48,029
Max!

1045
01:17:56,271 --> 01:17:58,398
Spike, come here.

1046
01:18:06,448 --> 01:18:08,250
No!

1047
01:18:08,250 --> 01:18:09,851
Get out.

1048
01:18:09,851 --> 01:18:11,182
He'll kill you.

1049
01:18:18,860 --> 01:18:19,986
Max.

1050
01:18:42,551 --> 01:18:43,813
Spike!

1051
01:21:01,022 --> 01:21:03,115
Max.

1052
01:21:37,826 --> 01:21:39,054
Get away from my dog.

1053
01:21:47,836 --> 01:21:49,827
Get away from him!

1054
01:21:51,439 --> 01:21:53,031
No!

1055
01:22:58,306 --> 01:23:01,042
Lori! Come here! You got
to come see this! Come on!

1056
01:23:01,042 --> 01:23:03,411
OK. Come on, Spike.

1057
01:23:03,411 --> 01:23:04,646
Let's say hi to Rudy.

1058
01:23:04,646 --> 01:23:05,947
Come on.

1059
01:23:05,947 --> 01:23:07,148
You won't believe this.
Come on.

1060
01:23:07,148 --> 01:23:09,250
What?

1061
01:23:09,250 --> 01:23:10,752
Surprise.

1062
01:23:10,752 --> 01:23:13,755
Oh, no! Look at them!

1063
01:23:13,755 --> 01:23:17,492
- Aren't they cute?
- Oh, come here.

1064
01:23:17,492 --> 01:23:19,761
Hey, you want one?
You want one?

1065
01:23:19,761 --> 01:23:22,321
Oh, look. Spike's jealous.

